text: Rumah Asun is a settlement in the Kanowit division of Sarawak, Malaysia. It lies approximately east of the state capital Kuching. Neighbouring settlements include: *Rumah Milang southeast *Rumah Adam northeast *Rumah Galau southwest *Rumah Jimban south *Rumah Siminai north *Rumah Tuba southeast *Rumah Beli northeast *Rumah Nyumbang southwest *Rumah Nyawai southwest *Rumah Penghulu Linau northwest ==References== Category:Populated places in Sarawak
title: Rumah Asun
